---
// About: headline, the animated "magic" Clarke quote, intro paragraphs + stats.
---
<section id="about" style="position:relative;z-index:2;border-top:1px solid var(--line,#23242e);background:var(--panel,#0c0d11);">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:110px 28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;">
    <div data-reveal>
      <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--red,#ff2a45);">02 / ABOUT</span>
      <h2 style="margin:16px 0 0;font-size:clamp(28px,3.4vw,46px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.01em;">
        I make machines that feel alive — light, motion and code in dialogue with the people around them.
      </h2>
      <figure style="margin:32px 0 0;position:relative;border-left:2px solid var(--red,#ff2a45);padding:4px 0 4px 20px;">
        <span style="position:absolute;left:-6px;top:8px;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red,#ff2a45);color:var(--red,#ff2a45);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:ledPulse 1.6s infinite;"></span>
        <blockquote style="margin:0;font-size:clamp(17px,1.7vw,21px);line-height:1.5;font-style:italic;color:var(--ink,#f3f4f8);">“Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from <span style="position:relative;display:inline-block;font-style:normal;color:var(--red,#ff2a45);background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--red,#ff2a45) 0%,var(--red,#ff2a45) 42%,#ffd9df 49%,#ffffff 50%,#ffd9df 51%,var(--red,#ff2a45) 58%,var(--red,#ff2a45) 100%);background-size:300% 100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;text-shadow:0 0 16px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:magicSweep 9s ease-in-out infinite,magicFlicker 9s linear infinite;">magic<span aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:-15px;top:-12px;font-size:12px;-webkit-text-fill-color:#fff;color:#fff;text-shadow:0 0 8px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:starTwinkle 4.5s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:.2s;">✦</span><span aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;right:-16px;top:-7px;font-size:15px;-webkit-text-fill-color:#fff;color:#fff;text-shadow:0 0 8px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:starTwinkle 5.3s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:1.7s;">✶</span><span aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;right:2px;bottom:-13px;font-size:11px;-webkit-text-fill-color:#ffd9df;color:#ffd9df;text-shadow:0 0 8px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:starTwinkle 4.9s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:3.2s;">✧</span><span aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:-9px;bottom:-12px;font-size:13px;-webkit-text-fill-color:#fff;color:#fff;text-shadow:0 0 8px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:starTwinkle 6.1s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:2.4s;">✦</span><span aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:50%;top:-17px;font-size:10px;-webkit-text-fill-color:#fff;color:#fff;text-shadow:0 0 8px var(--red,#ff2a45);animation:starTwinkle 5.7s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:4.4s;">✶</span></span>.”</blockquote>
        <figcaption style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--muted,#7c7e8a);">ARTHUR C. CLARKE <span style="opacity:.75;">— ALIE’S GUIDING LIGHT</span></figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:22px;">
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--muted,#9a9aa2);">I'm a creative technologist who builds across disciplines — designing custom electronics from schematic to firmware, developing custom addressable RGB LED systems, and fabricating the physical pieces myself on the CNC and 3D printer.</p>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--muted,#9a9aa2);">Today I'm Co-Founder of hello_miami, growing the city's largest tech community, alongside installation and experiential event work. Most weeks are split between shipping product and soldering one more strip of pixels.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:8px;">
        <div style="border:1px solid var(--line,#23242e);padding:18px;border-radius:6px;">
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:32px;color:var(--red,#ff2a45);text-shadow:0 0 14px var(--red,#ff2a45);">200+</div>
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--muted,#7c7e8a);margin-top:6px;">EVENTS&nbsp;HOSTED</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border:1px solid var(--line,#23242e);padding:18px;border-radius:6px;">
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:32px;color:var(--red,#ff2a45);text-shadow:0 0 14px var(--red,#ff2a45);">60+</div>
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--muted,#7c7e8a);margin-top:6px;">COUNTRIES&nbsp;SHIPPED</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border:1px solid var(--line,#23242e);padding:18px;border-radius:6px;">
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:32px;color:var(--red,#ff2a45);text-shadow:0 0 14px var(--red,#ff2a45);">12+</div>
          <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--muted,#7c7e8a);margin-top:6px;">YEARS</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
